===== Involved rules descriptions:

[iamf][Rule #19] id: assert-parameter-substream-consistency
Section 4
Parameter Substream consistency checks:
- Every Parameter Substream in the IA Sequence SHALL consist of the same number of Parameter Block OBUs.
- Every Parameter Block OBU SHALL have the same duration as its corresponding Audio Frame OBU under the same sample rate.

